text: Bobbie Phillips (born January 29, 1968)There are conflicting sources for the year of Phillips' birth. Film Reference, The New York Times and others give 1972 is an American actress and animal rights activist. Phillips was born in Charleston, South Carolina. She is known for her rols as Cam in Chameleon (1998) and as Julie Costello in the television legal drama Murder One. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:American stage actors Category:American animal rights activists Category:Actors from Charleston, South Carolina
